title: Geoff Moore & The Distance Discography 1984-2011 (16 Release
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
GEOFF MOORE & THE DISTANCE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 16 releases...

 * 1984 - Where Are The Other Nine
 * 1986 - Over The Edge
 * 1987 - The Distance
 * 1988 - A Place To Stand
 * 1988 - Jingle Bell Rock - Single
 * 1989 - Foundations
 * 1990 - Pure And Simple
 * 1992 - A Friend Like U
 * 1993 - Evolution
 * 1995 - Home Run
 * 1996 - Greatest Hits
 * 1997 - Threads
 * 1999 - Geoff Moore
 * 2002 - A Beautiful Sound
 * 2007 - Speak To Me
 * 2011 - Saying Grace

Geoff Moore is a contemporary Christian music artist and songwriter. He started recording as a solo artist in 1984. In 1987, he formed Geoff Moore and the Distance, who released eight albums and broke-up in 1998, with Moore continuing as a solo artist.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
